  "response": "Yes, there are instances where Indian celebrities have been noted for their resemblance to foreign celebrities. Here are a few examples:\n\n1. **Hrithik Roshan and Bradley Cooper**: Bollywood actor Hrithik Roshan is often compared to Hollywood star Bradley Cooper due to their similar facial features, especially their eyes and jawline.\n\n2. **Priyanka Chopra and Eva Mendes**: Indian actress Priyanka Chopra has been noted for her resemblance to American actress Eva Mendes. Both share similar facial structures and smiles.\n\n3. **Parineeti Chopra and Hayden Panettiere**: Bollywood actress Parineeti Chopra has been compared to American actress Hayden Panettiere because of their similar facial features and smile.\n\n4. **Esha Gupta and Angelina Jolie**: Indian actress Esha Gupta is often compared to Hollywood star Angelina Jolie, particularly for their strikingly similar facial features.\n\nThese comparisons are often subjective and based on public opinion, but they highlight some interesting similarities between Indian and foreign celebrities.",
